data.description: Returning to the market at NO FAULT to the seller-- COUNTRY PARADISE with INCOME potential! This property, built by the seller in 2012, is a harmonious blend of a equestrian farm and comfortable living: amenities include substantial CUSTOM MILLWORK, GRANITE counters, INSTANT HOT WATER heater, ENORMOUS CEILING HEIGHT and a DOUBLE primary bedrooms on the main floor. The OPEN-CONCEPT family room is anchored by a HUGE STONE WOODBURNING FIREPLACE, the go-to place to enjoy the change of seasons as well as a view to the kitchen and dining area crowned by a Tiffany-style chandelier. CUSTOM BUILT-IN CABINTERY offers extra storage or a place to show off your collection. Every bedroom has its own en suite bath and all rooms on the main floor have access to the WRAP-AROUND PORCH-- the sunset views overlooking the pasture should be stunning! More room for expansion is available in the TERRACE LEVEL unfinished basement -- imagine extra living space, a workshop or a place to house BIG KID TOYS if the don't fit in the KITCHEN LEVEL DETACHED GARAGE. Need a place for your HORSES or other 4-legged friends? The SIGNATURE RED BARN and surrounding corrals are ready to go! And between the pond, woods and trails, the recreational opportunities are boundless. Follow the drive behind the main house, and you'll find a sweet CABIN nestled in the woods. It has a studio set-up for living/kitchen/bedroom and its own full bath suitable for extra family or overflow guests and potential SHORT OR LONG TERM RENTAL opportunity!. Need more space for the kids? There's also a roomy treehouse (it's literally built around a tree!) for seasonal camp-outs. Trails and wildlife abound on the 33+ ACRE PROPERTY so schedule your appointment today!
